properties.Name: FinancialProductRating
properties.Description:
The financial product rating for the Financial Product for the associated period.

Ex:
Fitch Investors Service bond ratings:
------------------------------------------------
Highest quality = AAA
High quality = AA
Upper medium quality = A
Medium grade = BBB
Somewhat speculative = BB
Low grade, speculative = B
Low grade, default possible = CCC
Low grade, partial recovery possible = CC
Imminent default = C
Default = D
